            <h4 class="font-bold mt-2">Inputs:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-4 ml-6 mb-2">
                <li>Input: Input (Type: Boolean) <span class="text-red-500">*</span></li>
            </ul>
            <h4 class="font-bold">Outputs:</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-4 ml-6 mb-2">
                <li>Output: Output of the NOT operation (Type: Boolean)</li>
